OL,3,CNew report looks at mental health
OL,4,Cinequalities experienced by Black
OL,5,Ccommunities
OL,7,FA new report has explored the mental
OL,8,Fhealth inequalities experienced by
OL,9,FBlack communities in local services.
OL,11,FMind in Berkshire heard from more than
OL,12,F180 people on several key themes
OL,13,Frelating to Black people's access to
OL,14,Fmental health care and support.
OL,16,FBetween 2021 and 2023, data showed
OL,17,Fthat Black individuals were over three
OL,18,Ftimes more likely to be detained under
OL,19,Fthe Mental Health Act than white
OL,20,Findividuals in the county.
