OL,7,FDr. Kathryn MacDermott, SRO of the
OL,8,FMental Health Act Detentions Project
OL,9,Fat Berkshire Healthcare NHS Foundation
OL,10,FTrust, said: "Nationally and within
OL,11,FBerkshire, Black people are
OL,12,Fdisproportionately more likely to be
OL,13,Fdetained under the Mental Health Act
OL,14,F1983.
OL,16,F"For the last two years, Berkshire
OL,17,FHealthcare NHS Foundation Trust have
OL,18,Fhad a dedicated Mental Health Act
OL,19,FDetention project which aims to
OL,20,Funderstand and address these
OL,21,Flongstanding racial inequalities.
